00:20:17.633 --> 00:20:18.592
<c.japanese>&lrm;どうした 少年…</c.japanese>

00:20:18.675 --> 00:20:19.843
<c.japanese>&lrm;（コウ）ナズナちゃん</c.japanese>

00:20:21.595 --> 00:20:22.554
<c.japanese>&lrm;ちゃ…</c.japanese>

00:20:23.764 --> 00:20:26.266
<c.japanese>&lrm;…って 呼んでもいいですか？
&lrm;これから</c.japanese>

00:20:26.350 --> 00:20:28.852
<c.japanese>&lrm;少しでも仲良くなれるように</c.japanese>

00:20:28.936 --> 00:20:32.522
<c.japanese>&lrm;あと トランシーバーで
&lrm;呼びかける時とか…</c.japanese>

00:20:34.274 --> 00:20:35.859
<c.japanese>&lrm;ガチ照れじゃないですか</c.japanese>

00:20:37.069 --> 00:20:38.487
<c.japanese>&lrm;ねえ ナズナちゃん</c.japanese>

00:20:38.570 --> 00:20:40.072
<c.japanese>&lrm;（ナズナ）
&lrm;いや “さん”だろ そこは</c.japanese>

00:20:40.155 --> 00:20:41.448
<c.japanese>&lrm;“さん”だろ そこは！</c.japanese>

00:20:41.531 --> 00:20:44.660
<c.japanese>&lrm;まずは 友達から始めてみようかと</c.japanese>

00:20:46.578 --> 00:20:48.372
<c.japanese>&lrm;友達なんか いねーくせに</c.japanese>

00:20:49.248 --> 00:20:50.332
<c.japanese>&lrm;（コウ）ヘヘ</c.japanese>

00:20:59.716 --> 00:21:01.635
<c.japanese>&lrm;そういえば…</c.japanese>

00:21:02.719 --> 00:21:07.224
<c.japanese>&lrm;この“悲しみのトランシーバー”
&lrm;結局 どうなったんだろう</c.japanese>

00:21:07.307 --> 00:21:09.601
<c.japanese>&lrm;誰か まだ持ってたりするのかな</c.japanese>

00:21:10.435 --> 00:21:11.520
<c.japanese>&lrm;それはないか</c.japanese>

00:21:11.603 --> 00:21:12.938
<c.japanese>&lrm;（コール音）</c.japanese>

00:21:13.522 --> 00:21:14.356
<c.japanese>&lrm;ナズナちゃ…</c.japanese>

00:21:15.482 --> 00:21:16.316
<c.japanese>&lrm;違…</c.japanese>

00:21:16.984 --> 00:21:18.402
<c.japanese>&lrm;こっちだ　なんで…</c.japanese>

00:21:18.485 --> 00:21:19.361
<c.japanese>&lrm;（アキラ）夜守</c.japanese>

00:21:19.444 --> 00:21:20.320
<c.japanese>&lrm;あっ</c.japanese>

